# Canonical QA And Delivery

## QA

- QA is required for code, runtime, user-facing, or integration changes.
- The QA plan should match the changed surface and configured dev runtime.
- Start command: `{{ dev.startCommand }}`
- Runtime URL: `{{ dev.startUrl }}`
- QA may be skipped only with an explicit state reason.

