## Delivery

- Delivery must report whether the work reached the configured integration branch: `{{ git.integrationBranch }}`.
- Release branch: `{{ git.releaseBranch }}`.
- Delivery must record commit or PR identifiers when available.
- Delivery must update configured docs when the shipped behavior changes repo truth.
- Final reporting separates implementation, release, and local workspace cleanup facts.
